description: A rare South Boston offering, this 1-bedroom residence boasts a versatile bonus room—perfect as an office, nursery, or guest space—and features a private wrap-around deck with direct access to a fenced yard, ideal for pets! Perfectly located on a quiet side street steps to the Red Line, this exceptional residence offers central AC/heat, gas fireplace, 9' ceilings, newer in-unit LG ThinQ washer + dryer, hardwood floors, recessed lighting, black granite counters, cherry cabinetry, stainless appliances, and a large private locked storage unit. Easy access to Mass Pike/93, steps to Andrew Sq MBTA, and close to South Bay, Seaport, Broadway, and the upcoming Washington Village Development. Enjoy proximity to popular spots like Tatte Cafe and Castle Island Brewing, plus other new cafes and restaurants, and just a 5-min walk to the beach!
